'''瓦內薩·吉倫'''（{{lang-en|Vanessa Guillen}}）是[[美国|美国]][[德克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]][[胡德堡|胡德堡]]的一位20歲女兵，她于2020年4月22日在[[營房|营房]]停车场失踪。在吉伦失踪之前，她告诉家人，她曾經被胡德堡的一名[[中士|中士]][[性骚扰|性骚扰]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Reward for missing soldier Vanessa Guillen grows to over $50,000 after Latino group and rapper add to it|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/06/17/us/vanessa-guillen-missing-soldier-reward-baby-bash-trnd/index.html|author=Lee|date=2020-06-17|first=Alicia|work=CNN|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209180146/https://www.cnn.com/2020/06/17/us/vanessa-guillen-missing-soldier-reward-baby-bash-trnd/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過吉倫並未透露這名中士的名字。吉倫母亲建议举报性騷擾的中士，但吉倫表示，此前也有遭到性騷擾的女兵舉報該名中士，不過均被開除。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Salma Hayek uses social media to find missing US Army soldier Vanessa Guillen|url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/salma-hayek-social-media-missing-us-soldier-vanessa-guillen|accessdate=|author=McCarthy|date=2020-06-15|first=Tyler|work=Fox News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330162519/https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/salma-hayek-social-media-missing-us-soldier-vanessa-guillen|archivedate=2021-03-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=‘How can you not have these answers?’: Reward reaches $50K as desperate search for missing Fort Hood soldier Vanessa Guillen continues|url=https://www.crimeonline.com/2020/06/17/how-can-you-not-have-these-answers-reward-reaches-50k-as-desperate-search-for-missing-fort-hood-soldier-vanessa-guillen-continues/|author=Egan|date=2020-06-17|first=Leigh|work=CrimeOnline|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928065811/https://www.crimeonline.com/2020/06/17/how-can-you-not-have-these-answers-reward-reaches-50k-as-desperate-search-for-missing-fort-hood-soldier-vanessa-guillen-continues/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Reward for missing Fort Hood soldier Vanessa Guillen doubles to $50,000|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/vanessa-guillen-missing-fort-hood-soldier-50000-reward/|author=Brito|date=2020-06-17|first=Christopher|work=CBS News|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209071347/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/vanessa-guillen-missing-fort-hood-soldier-50000-reward/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。吉倫担心如果向母亲透露中士的姓名，母親會舉報中士，這樣反而會導致母親遭到報復。几周后，瓦內薩失踪了。2020年7月1日，吉倫的家人在新聞發佈會上表示，在胡德堡附近发现了一具尸體，該尸体很可能是吉倫本人<ref name="Remains">{{Cite web|title=Remains of missing soldier Vanessa Guillén likely found, family says, as suspect kills himself|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/2020/07/01/vanessa-guillen-remains/|accessdate=2020-07-02|author=Horton|date=2020-07-01|first=Alex|work=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|8=|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125165728/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/2020/07/01/vanessa-guillen-remains/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同一天，技术兵罗宾逊（Aaron David Robinson）在警方试图逮捕时自杀<ref name="Remains" />。經調查，吉倫於2020年4月在胡德堡被人用锤子打死<ref>{{cite news |title=20岁女兵惨死 美军胡德堡基地14人遭解雇或停职 |url=https://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/12-09/9357846.shtml |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108125422/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/12-09/9357846.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。     

